\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 Cultural Legacy\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Miranda Priestly became a template for the "icy powerful woman" archetype in pop culture. Meryl Streep won a Golden Globe for the role and received an Academy Award nomination. The character is frequently cited in discussions of workplace power, gender and ambition, and what it costs women to reach the top of their fields.\
